        "endTime": 12.288,
        "duration": 4.413,
        "sentenceIndex": 12
      },
      {
        "text": "Her cousin walked in and dropped her drink.",
        "startTime": 12.288,
        "endTime": 15.394,
        "duration": 3.107,
        "sentenceIndex": 13
      },
      {
        "text": "Sarah said, \"Oh my God, it looks like you are dead.",
