        "duration": 4.07,
        "sentenceIndex": 41
      },
      {
        "text": "That was the most painful thing that ever happened to him.",
        "startTime": 8.654,
        "endTime": 12.869,
        "duration": 4.215,
        "sentenceIndex": 42
      },
      {
        "text": "They told Jake's parents he has three months to live.",
        "startTime": 12.869,
        "endTime": 16.721,
        "duration": 3.852,
        "sentenceIndex": 43
      },
      {
