        "endTime": 13.12,
        "duration": 3.247,
        "sentenceIndex": 57
      },
      {
        "text": "He has fourteen days to live for the second time.",
        "startTime": 13.12,
        "endTime": 17.199,
        "duration": 4.079,
        "sentenceIndex": 58
      },
      {
        "text": "Jake was the only person with both types of cancer.",
