        "endTime": 6.936,
        "duration": 2.074,
        "sentenceIndex": 61
      },
      {
        "text": "He went to bed and did not know if he would wake up.",
        "startTime": 6.936,
        "endTime": 10.655,
        "duration": 3.718,
        "sentenceIndex": 62
      },
      {
        "text": "His future was right there and maybe the next day.",
        "startTime": 10.655,
        "endTime": 14.23,
        "duration": 3.575,
        "sentenceIndex": 63
      },
      {
        "text": "Jake understood something important.",
