        "endTime": 12.939,
        "duration": 5.922,
        "sentenceIndex": 67
      },
      {
        "text": "Sarah woke up in the hospital and saw her black feet.",
        "startTime": 12.939,
        "endTime": 17.488,
        "duration": 4.549,
        "sentenceIndex": 68
      },
      {
        "text": "They wheeled Sarah into the room to take her legs.",
